    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，两个section。那\"Go to work\"这部分具体包含哪些任务？每个任务需要标注参与者和满意度评分吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section Go to work",
