      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我按这个结构来画：标题My working day，两个section分别是Go to work和Go home，所有任务和评分都按你说的设置，无障碍描述也加上了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "section Go to work",
